MSB2K

MSB2K.Rd

Dataset for core MSB2K as provided in the package rbacon

Usage

MSB2K

Format

A data frame with 40 rows and 4 variables:

labID

factor Sample ID number from the lab.

age

integer Radiocarbon age.

error

integer Age uncertainty in years.

depth

double Depth in core in cm.

Details

The example dataset MSB2K as provided by the rbacon package.

References

Blaauw, Maarten, and J. Andrés Christen. 2011. Flexible Paleoclimate Age-Depth Models Using an Autoregressive Gamma Process. Bayesian Analysis 6 (3): 457-74. doi:10.1214/ba/1339616472

Maarten Blaauw, J. Andres Christen and Marco A. Aquino L. (2020). rbacon: Age-Depth Modelling using Bayesian Statistics. R package version 2.4.3. https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=rbacon
